data.description: This well-maintained 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath move-in ready home is nestled in the neighborhood of Hamilton Green, Charlotte, NC. Perfect for home buyers looking for their dream home and no rental restrictions for the investor buyer.  This home exudes a charming elegance with natural light creating a warm & inviting atmosphere. Upon entry, you'll appreciate the expansive family room with fireplace, perfect for relaxing times and entertaining. The eat-in kitchen with breakfast bar welcomes you to prepare meals with plenty of space. The large primary BR features a spacious walk-in closet and the ensuite bath has garden tub that adds a touch of luxury.  Outside, the expansive front yard and backyard offer space for outdoor activities & peaceful times. This home is truly a haven of comfort & style, perfect for those seeking a peaceful & stylish living experience. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this exceptional property yours! 3D Tour:  https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=ziC4W4wy6mK
